
-------------------------------------------
|||| Packets Twist PLugin Installation ||||
-------------------------------------------


Default:
 - twister server side path: /opt/twister
 - twister client side path: /home/user/twister


	---- SERVER side ----

1. sudo cp /path/to/PacketsTwistPlugin/PacketSniffer /opt/twister/plugins

2. vim /path/to/twister/config/plugins.xml

!!!! This plugin name must be 'SNIFF' in order to be recognized !!!!

append config:

<Plugin>
	<name>SNIFF</name>
	<jarfile>PacketSniffer/PacketsTwistPlugin.jar</jarfile>
	<pyfile>PacketSniffer/PacketsTwistPlugin.py</pyfile>
	<status>enabled</status>
	<property>
		<propname>historyLength</propname>
		<propvalue>4000</propvalue>
	</property>
	<property>
		<propname>packetsBuffer</propname>
		<propvalue>400</propvalue>
	</property>
</Plugin>


	---- CLIENT side ----

1. cp /path/to/PacketsTwistPlugin/PacketsTwist /path/to/twister/services

2. cp /path/to/PacketsTwistPlugin/start_packets_twist.py /path/to/twister/bin

